text:
So, I changed right away.
How does it look?

It looks great...!
It suits you well.
It seems like Natsuha is pleased too.

Yes, very much so! I wonder why it's so exciting
to put on a new costume!

I'm always working out, stretching,
and toning my body...
Maybe it's also for moments like this...

I'm also looking forward to seeing Natsuha
wearing this costume on stage.
Don't miss the chance to see the new me...!
